high_descs: Go straight and immediately left into the large room, going to the wall, then right again towards the kitchen area, turning right slightly to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Exit the kitchen the way you came in and go through the large room, taking the first left past the white table, then left again, and the first left again into the bedroom.
Slice the potato on the bed.
Return to the kitchen where you got the knife and stop at the cabinet with the microwave on it.
Place the knife inside the cabinets.
Return to the bedroom with the sliced potato.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Go back to the kitchen again, stopping at the same microwave.
Use the microwave on the potato slice and remove it.
Turn around towards the sink.
Place the potato slice into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of potato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head right to reach the sink.

Cut the potato on the bed with the knife.
Turn right to exit the room and turn right to reach the kitchen and reach the cabinet under the microwave on the right.
Put the knife in the cabinet.
Head right and turn left to reach the bedroom and face the bed on the right.
Pick up the slice of potato from the bed.
Turn right to exit the room and head right to reach the kitchen and reach the microwave on the right.
Heat the slice of potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to reach the sink.
Put the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of potato in the sink.
